                                <date>1958</date>. С. <biblScope unit="page">??–??</biblScope>.</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><xi:include href="../encodingdesc.xml" parse="xml"/></teiHeader><text><body><entry xml:id="entry_idæwun" xml:lang="os-x-digor"><form type="lemma"><orth>idæwun</orth></form><usg><lang/></usg><sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru"><q>отрицать</q></abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en"><q>disclaim</q></abv:tr></sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru"><q>отпираться</q></abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en"><q>deny</q></abv:tr></sense></sense><re><form xml:lang="os-x-iron" type="lemma"><orth>dæwccag</orth></form><form xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>idæwccag</orth></form><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru"><q>спорный</q></abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en"><q>disputable</q></abv:tr></sense></re><abv:exampleGrp><abv:example><quote>færsuj sæ radugaj, æma sæ fuldæretæ ǧavtoncæ idæwunmæ</quote><abv:tr xml:lang="ru"><q>(судья) спрашивает их по очереди, но большинство пытались отрицать (свое преступление)</q></abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en"><q>(the judge) asks them by turn, but the majority tried to deny (their crime)</q></abv:tr><bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_SD"/><biblScope>193%l2%l</biblScope></bibl></abv:example></abv:exampleGrp><etym xml:lang="ru">Может быть, восходит к *%ivī-dav%i-; ср. <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/> <w>dav-</w> <gloss><q>говорить</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/> <w>davastan</w> <gloss><q>говорить</q></gloss></mentioned>. Вряд ли от %idaw%i ‘обвинение’, ‘тяжба’. См. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ædæwagæ"/>.%n<bibl><author>Benveniste,</author><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_BSL"/><biblScope>LII 13</biblScope></bibl> 13.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">May be it traces back to *%ivī-dav%i-; cf. <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/> <w>dav-</w> <gloss><q>to say</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/> <w>davastan</w> <gloss><q>talk</q></gloss></mentioned>. It is hardly from %idaw%i ‘accusation’, ‘suit’. See <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ædæwagæ"/>.%n<bibl><author>Benveniste,</author><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_BSL"/><biblScope>LII 13</biblScope></bibl> 13.</etym></entry></body></text></TEI>